msgid "Ah Caleb… no. Please refrain from breaking any cameras."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/WW_Maintenance_Deeper_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Ah we’re unfortunately a bit deeper than I anticipated…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BS_KKStage1_Lines_Index6_Line"
msgid ""
"Ah! And it looks like we’re going to play a little precautionary game. Quite "
"a simple one really."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/WW_Maintenance_Detour_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid ""
"Ah! The Breakroom! Yes, the Breakroom. I'm certain that's the way we went "
