msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_WalterIntro_ROT_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Ah, Welcome to Walter…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BH_Intro_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid ""
"Ah, but it looks like we’ll need to quickly address one last safety measure "
"before we get fully reestablished on our designated path."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/WW_Maintenance_Redirect_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Ah, come on Caleb... We have so much more ahead of us..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_Reinforce_0_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Ah, here we are."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_Maintenance_FoundWW_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Ah, it looks like we're here…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BS_Redirect_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Ah, let's not waste time..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_SmileEncounter_Maintenance_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Ah, see? Nothing to worry over at all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_FunOMeter_Intro_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Ah, the Fun-O-Meter. A perfect stop on our joy filled journey. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_ROT_Rejoin_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Ah, there we are… It seems you got a bit distracted back there…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_Maintenance_SmileEscape_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid ""
"Ah, well! Just in time aren't we… A bit close for comfort, but we made it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BS_LovelyPainting_Pt1_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Ah, what a lovely painting..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt ""
"NarrationTextData/WW_DeepStorage_Decision_Disobey_Pt1_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Ah- Caleb please- no, not there. This isn't where we need to go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BS_AlternateDestination_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid ""
"Ah... Please follow the illuminated arrows to our alternate destination."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_WalterIntro_ROT_Lines_Index5_Line"
msgid "Ahm -excuse me... Let’s move on…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/WW_MemoryMeterNudge_Pt4_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Ahm- Caleb… I believe you’ve left something behind…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/ES_Introduction_SNF_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid "Ahm- I imagine you’re feeling a tad disoriented... "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BS_Intro_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Ahm- I see you’ve centered your attention on our childhood basement."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BS_LovelyPainting_Pt3_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid ""
"Ahm- Imagine all the time and effort that went into making that painting "
"look just how it does now. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BS_KKStage1_Lines_Index10_Line"
msgid "Ahm- you’ve got this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_ThroatClear_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Ahm."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/WW_MemoryMeterNudge_Pt2_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Ahm..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/WW_WonderOff_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid ""
"Ahm... I see you've managed to find a rather gloomy corner in this otherwise "
"joy-filled memory."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_EmotionalEncouragement_1_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid ""
"Ahm... Not to worry, while you do currently seem to be quite lost. I’m sure, "
"eventually, you’ll figure it all out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BH_MemoryDisposal_Pt2_Lines_Index3_Line"
msgid "All to keep you happy…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/ES_Introduction_Lines_Index14_Line"
msgid ""
"All you need to do is focus. Maybe there’s a specific plant you remember "
"from your parents’ bedroom,"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_Maintenance_Trapped_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Alright, not to worry! Our mind is just having a bit of fun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BS_END_Stage1_Pt2_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Alright, you remember that little game we played?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/ES_Introduction_SNF_Lines_Index7_Line"
msgid "And actually, that’s precisely why you're here..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_ROT_Rejoin_Lines_Index3_Line"
msgid "And bear no truth or substance whatsoever."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BH_MemoryDisposal_Pt2_Lines_Index4_Line"
msgid "And for what?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/ES_Introduction_Lines_Index12_Line"
msgid ""
"And that’s precisely where we’re going. To go capture that very essence of "
"joy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/ES_Introduction_SNF_Lines_Index5_Line"
msgid ""
"And this vast void of nothingness that we are currently floating in, is your "
"mind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_ROT_Rejoin_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid "Before we continue, I should remind you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BH_DetHalls_Pt4_Lines_Index2_Line"
msgid "But I can see you’re not going to listen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BH_Intro_Lines_Index2_Line"
msgid "But I'm quite certain you'll find it entirely manageable..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_EmotionalEncouragement_3_Lines_Index2_Line"
msgid ""
"But in fact, considering the abnormally large amount of time you've already "
"spent on this puzzle,"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/WW_MemoryLoop_Nudge_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid "But it’s ok, we’ve been here before haven’t we..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/WW_MemoryLoop_Intro_Lines_Index2_Line"
msgid ""
"But no need to worry… by doing something out of the ordinary or unexpected, "
"we should be able to break the cycle,"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/WW_DeepStorage_LockedDoor_Lines_Index4_Line"
msgid "But not to worry, nothing here is ever truly shut out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/ES_Introduction_SNF_Lines_Index3_Line"
msgid "But not to worry... This is perfectly normal."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/ES_Introduction_Lines_Index6_Line"
msgid ""
"But not to worry... This is perfectly normal. To start, your name is "
"Caleb... And this vast void of nothingness that we are currently floating "
"in, is your mind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_MemoryLoop_Nudge2_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid "But please Caleb, we have places to be."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BS_END_Stage2_Lines_Index3_Line"
msgid "But please rest assured, we've again come entirely prepared for this…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_WalterIntro_Maintenance_Lines_Index4_Line"
msgid ""
"But please take caution, as even though he has always played a crucial and "
"irreplaceable role in our childhood as our sole unwavering companion..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BS_KKStage1_Lines_Index3_Line"
msgid "But please, don’t worry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/ER_Switch1_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid "But please, let’s not interact with any more mysterious switches."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/WW_Slide#1_Redirect_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid "But there are more memories waiting."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_Maintenance_SmileEscape_Lines_Index3_Line"
msgid ""
"But these little intrusions are actually harmless, and completely made up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_EmotionalEncouragement_8_Lines_Index3_Line"
msgid ""
"But, despite this, might I remind you of the many joy-filled memories yet to "
"come on our maintenance route."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_FunOMeter_Intro_Lines_Index2_Line"
msgid ""
"But, given your demonstrated proclivity for resolving unexpected challenges, "
"I’m sure you can figure it out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_EmotionalEncouragement_2_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid "But, might I remind you, that this little setback is just that… "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/WW_ROTSpill_Pt2_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid ""
"But, we can fix this… Please continue directly toward the large secondary "
"slide tower."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BS_END_Stage2_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "CALEB STOP I-"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_Intro_ROT_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "CALEB! WHAT ARE YOU DOING!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/ER_Erase_Pt3_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Caleb! Please… Let’s get back to our maintenance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/ER_Confirm_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Caleb… What- how did you get here?..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/WW_ROTSpill_Pt1_Lines_Index4_Line"
msgid "Certainly not the sort of thing we want crowding this lovely memory."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_Redirect_0_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Come on Caleb, we have so much more waiting for us..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BH_DetHalls_Pt5_Lines_Index2_Line"
msgid ""
"Continuing to seep in and fester, until it eventually consumes everything we "
"hold dear."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_FunOMeter_Retry_Pt6_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Deep breath in…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_FunOMeter_Retry_Pt6_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid "Deep breath out…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_SecurityCamKnockOff_2_Lines_Index2_Line"
msgid "Destroying them will bring no benefit whatsoever."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/WW_Slide#3_Redirect_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Don't worry about that, it's just a little mess..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_FunOMeter_Retry_Pt1_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Don’t worry Caleb, we have plenty of time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_EmotionalEncouragement_8_Lines_Index4_Line"
msgid ""
"Each one brimming with that uncomplicated joy that makes life… worth it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_SecurityCamKnockOff_0_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid "Emotional Maintenance & Diagnostic Regulation system."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BH_MemoryDisposal_Pt2_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid "Everything I’ve built for you…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BH_MemoryDisposal_Pt2_Lines_Index2_Line"
msgid "Everything I’ve buried for you…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_PlayplaceIntro_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid ""
"Everything here has been tirelessly tested and is guaranteed to be "
"completely safe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/WW_DeepStorage_Decision_Obey_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Excellent, Caleb."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BH_Intro_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid ""
"Excellent. We’ve successfully arrived in our recollection of the Bounce "
"House…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/ES_Introduction_Lines_Index16_Line"
msgid ""
"Focus on that, and suddenly, you might find yourself in the middle of that "
"very park again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_SmileEncounter_Maintenance_Lines_Index4_Line"
msgid ""
"For now, let’s take a slight discretionary detour, and center our focus on "
"something a bit more productive."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_WonderOff_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Haha, there you are..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BH_DetHalls_Pt1_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Haha.. Our mind has made quite a mess hasn’t it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_EmotionalEncouragement_2_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid ""
"Having a bit of trouble again are we? You seem to be temporarily stuck. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_WalterIntro_Maintenance_Lines_Index5_Line"
msgid "He is rather delicate, and requires the utmost care and restraint."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/ES_Introduction_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Hello. I- wait- no-..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/ES_Introduction_SNF_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Hello. I- wait- no-..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/ES_Introduction_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid ""
"Hello. I.. am you... Or rather, a particularly articulate aspect of you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/WW_Intro_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Here we are. Welcome to our memory of the Waterworks…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_EmotionalEncouragement_4_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Hi. I'm just popping in to let you know… You're doing great."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_EmotionalEncouragement_6_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid ""
"Hi. I’m just quickly popping in to remind you, don’t be afraid to have some "
"fun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BS_KKInterruption_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Hm... I’m sure it’s nothing. Here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BH_KeycardCloset_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Hm... Unfortunately it looks like we'll need to momentarily part ways."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_FunOMeter_Retry_Pt3_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid ""
"Hmm… I believe you do need to shoot the foam cubes into that great big "
"funnel…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/WW_DeepStorage_Initial_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "Hmm… It looks like we have… Diverted slightly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/WW_DeepStorage_LockedDoor_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid ""
"Hm… It would seem we’ve inadvertently drifted into a section of our memory "
"that our mind has chosen to… set aside."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/ES_Introduction_Lines_Index13_Line"
msgid ""
"How do we access these memories? Another great question... It’s quite simple."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/ES_Introduction_Lines_Index10_Line"
msgid "How do we get that joy? I’m glad you asked..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BH_DetHalls_Pt5_Lines_Index6_Line"
msgid ""
"However, in the event you just can’t seem to focus, despite numerous polite "
"and warm hearted reminders,"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BH_MemoryMeterBreak_Lines_Index3_Line"
msgid ""
"However, rest assured we’ve come prepared for this. Please continue through "
"the unmarked door to your right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_Intro_Maintenance_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid ""
"However, this memory does appear to be quite full of joy, and should in fact "
"be the perfect place to continue filling up our memory meter."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_EmotionalEncouragement_3_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid "I assure you these feelings are completely valid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BH_DetHalls_Pt5_Lines_Index4_Line"
msgid "I can assure you there is absolutely no cause for concern."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/ER_Jump_Lines_Index2_Line"
msgid "I can find another way… I- I can! Please! I DON'T WANT TO-"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BH_DetHalls_Pt4_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid ""
"I do have to remind you, that these lingering feelings of guilt and "
"emptiness are nothing to worry about."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_EmotionalEncouragement_3_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "I imagine you might currently be experiencing feelings of frustration."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_EmotionalEncouragement_5_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid ""
"I imagine you're currently feeling quite stuck... But remember, we’ve been "
"through all of this before."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BS_KKStage1_Lines_Index2_Line"
msgid "I imagine you’re feeling a bit unsettled."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_EmotionalEncouragement_8_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "I know at times it can be discouraging..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_EmotionalEncouragement_0_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "I see you're having a bit of trouble…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_MemoryLoop_Nudge2_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "I see you’re finding this hall quite amusing…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_WonderOff_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid "I see you’ve found a little crack in our joy-filled maintenance route."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_Maintenance_SmileEscape_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid ""
"I suppose now would be a great time to continue our discussion on those "
"precautions that we skipped over earlier."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BH_MemoryDisposal_Pt1_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid "I told you to STAY PUT!!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_SecurityCamKnockOff_3_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid ""
"I understand they can be unnerving, but please rest assured they watch over "
"us with only our very best interests in mind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BS_Intro_Lines_Index4_Line"
msgid "I'll be back momentarily."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BS_END_Stage2_Lines_Index10_Line"
msgid "I'll be back momentarily…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_Maintenance_Trapped_Lines_Index2_Line"
msgid "I'll be right here, silently cheering you on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_EmotionalEncouragement_7_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid ""
"I'm just popping in to let you know… Whatever it is you are currently doing, "
"you’re doing it wonderfully."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_MemoryLoop_Intro_Alternate_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid "I'm sure you can figure this out. I'll be back momentarily."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_Intro_ROT_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid "I- I'm sorry... I was getting quite worried there for a minute."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/ES_Introduction_Lines_Index2_Line"
msgid ""
"I.. am your conscience. Your sense of direction. That faint voice on your "
"shoulder that whispers, perhaps that slice of cake is a bit unnecessarily "
"wide?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_MemoryLoop_Nudge1_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "If this hall seems familiar, it’s because it is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_SecurityCameraIntro_Lines_Index4_Line"
msgid ""
"If you are to ever come across something unpleasant feeling again, or "
"possibly anything relating to the inescapable dread of rotting past memories,"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_Intro_ROT_Lines_Index4_Line"
msgid ""
"If you see anything like that again, please immediately turn away and pay "
"absolutely no attention to it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/ER_Erase_Pt2_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid ""
"Imagine that winding lazy river in the Waterworks, or the Playplace and all "
"the… all the wonderful… "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_WalterIntro_ROT_Lines_Index3_Line"
msgid "In a moment, you’ll get to actually hold her..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_WalterIntro_Maintenance_Lines_Index3_Line"
msgid "In a moment, you’ll get to actually hold him again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_SecurityCamKnockOff_3_Lines_Index2_Line"
msgid ""
"In fact, I’d like you to try a visualization exercise. Instead of cameras, "
"please try imagining them as small, affectionate birds nesting in the "
"ceiling."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BH_DetHalls_Pt5_Lines_Index5_Line"
msgid ""
"In routine, simply staying focused on the joys of life renders that mold "
"entirely inert."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/ES_Introduction_Lines_Index9_Line"
msgid ""
"In these times, we, or you rather, need to pop in and give it a small "
"infusion of joy, a nudge, really, to get the gears of our mind back into "
"motion."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_Intro_Maintenance_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid ""
"It appears we’ve experienced a minor navigational error. We seem to have "
"skipped forward."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BS_KKStage2_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "It appears your focus is ever so slightly slipping…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/WW_MemoryLoop_Intro_Lines_Index0_Line"
