msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BH_DetHalls_Pt5_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid ""
"You see, much like the mold on that sandwich, if given the opportunity, this "
"rot will begin to spread…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_Maintenance_SmileEscape_Lines_Index2_Line"
msgid ""
"You see, sometimes our mind can be a bit eccentric and imagine little "
"scenarios that can get a tad dark."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/ES_Introduction_Lines_Index8_Line"
msgid ""
"You see, sometimes our mind can get a bit gummed up, running low on that "
"pure, uncomplicated joy that makes life worth it..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_Maintenance_SmileEscape_Lines_Index5_Line"
msgid ""
"You’d never actually do it of course, but those thoughts are there "
"nonetheless. Just little tangents our mind runs off with to entertain itself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_EmotionalEncouragement_0_Lines_Index2_Line"
msgid "You’re doing wonderfully."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_FunOMeter_Retry_Pt5_Lines_Index0_Line"
msgid "You’re having quite a bit of trouble aren’t you?"
msgstr ""

