msgid "You’ve again gotten yourself stuck in a memory loop."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/WW_MemoryLoop_Intro_Lines_Index3_Line"
msgid "and pop ourselves right back on path."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_EmotionalEncouragement_8_Lines_Index2_Line"
msgid "can make you feel like there's something fundamentally wrong with you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_SecurityCamKnockOff_2_Lines_Index1_Line"
msgid ""
"designed specifically to ensure our re-experiencing remains as joy-filled as "
"possible..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/BH_Lost_Lines_Index3_Line"
msgid ""
"every mistake, every misdirection, every DISTRACTION you’ve entertained,"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_SecurityCameraIntro_Lines_Index2_Line"
msgid ""
"has now been successfully reinstated after nearly a full year of "
"retirement..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/CM_Maintenance_SmileEscape_Lines_Index7_Line"
msgid ""
"it’s best we stay away, and set our focus on the joy-filled parts of our "
"mind…"
msgstr ""

