msgid ""
"please immediately flip the switch in the associated doorway to toggle the "
"protocol."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "NarrationTextData/GL_SecurityCameraIntro_Lines_Index5_Line"
msgid ""
"please immediately turn away from whatever it is, and focus solely on this "
"wonderfully complex and overarching safety system."
